    <h1>Why guinea fowl has dots</h1>
  </div>
<p>There was a time when guinea fowl did not have dots in her feathers. She was an adventurous bird and loved to discover things. One day tortoise challenged her to find out why the top of the jungle's one and only mountain was always shining. Guinea fowl could not resist this as curiosity got the better of her. Off she went, over the desert, past the ocean, up to the very top of the mountain where she indeed did discover why the mountain top shines:snow. Guinea Fowl was the first ever animal to see snow.</p>
    
